smart-surveillance/
│── app/
│   ├── __init__.py          # Initialize Flask app, DB, blueprints
│   ├── config.py            # Configurations (Dev, Prod)
│   ├── models.py            # Database models
│   ├── extensions.py        # For initializing db, login_manager, etc.
│   │
│   ├── routes/              # App routes (modularized blueprints)
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   ├── dashboard.py     # Dashboard routes
│   │   ├── cameras.py       # Camera feeds & snapshots
│   │   ├── logs.py          # Intrusion logs
│   │   ├── auth.py          # Authentication (optional)
│   │
│   ├── services/            # ML, notification, utility services
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   ├── detection.py     # Object detection / intrusion logic
│   │   ├── notifications.py # WhatsApp/SMS/email alerts
│   │   ├── storage.py       # Save/retrieve snapshots
│   │
│   ├── static/              # Static files
│   │   ├── css/             # Tailwind generated CSS
│   │   ├── js/              # Custom JS (if any)
│   │   ├── images/          # Snapshots & assets
│   │
│   ├── templates/           # HTML Templates (Jinja + Tailwind)
│   │   ├── base.html        # Common layout
│   │   ├── dashboard.html   # Dashboard with camera feeds
│   │   ├── logs.html        # Logs page with search/filter
│   │   ├── cameras.html     # List of cameras
│   │   ├── login.html       # Login page (optional)
│   │
│   └── utils/               # Helpers
│       ├── __init__.py
│       ├── image_utils.py   # Enhance/resize/compress images
│       ├── time_utils.py    # Time formatting helpers
│
│── migrations/              # Flask-Migrate (DB migrations)
│
│── instance/                # Local DB configs (ignored by Git)
│
│── tests/                   # Unit tests
│
│── venv/                    # Virtual environment (ignored by Git)
│
│── run.py                   # Main entry point
│── requirements.txt         # Dependencies
│── README.md                # Project documentation
